Invocation Name: exicom charger
des:
EVA is an virtual assistant agent of Exicom. EVA can help you to know more about Exicom and its values and products. EVA is also IOT enabled with AC Type2 EV Charger for remote start and stop. User can use Alexa to give commands to EV chargers provided by Exicom.
You can ask any query to about Exicom, Its products, Services and many more. Gradually EVA is collating more information for customer support and service model where customer can directly charge the vehicle on just a simple command to Alexa.
